/>\n5：手淫的男孩，根本就不懂得戀愛，這個問題已經被手淫的惡習給矇蔽了。"},{"pid":"44a6b8cbd977eb03da8ac282039751f19c6cf58b","tid":335683,"uid":72867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T19:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後女神搵你出嚟飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醉到要你送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就四個月份量一次過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9eb3090c2c9d20e3e07154b46243527aecf5d3d","tid":335683,"uid":111088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T19:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>然後女神搵你出嚟飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醉到要你送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就四個月份量一次過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟啦<br />\n再幻想吓女神嘅迷人身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n銷魂嘅叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0145dd705afce98869fa7abbd58539501c721a8b","tid":335683,"uid":72867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T19:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>然後女神搵你出嚟飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醉到要你送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就四個月份量一次過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟啦<br />\n再幻想吓女神嘅迷人身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n銷魂嘅